These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, potato, cucumber, grapes
1. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | apricot | potato | cucumber | grapes |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, juice, sprite
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | almond-milk | sprite | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, chess, dancing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | dancing | chess | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, western, family
1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | martial-arts | family | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
