1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | climbing | baseball | rowing | skateboarding |

