.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, punk, techno, gospel
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | techno | punk | house | gospel |

 